  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "I've found a friend in Jesus, He's everything to me.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 49
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He's the fairest of ten thousand to my soul;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The Lily of the Valley in Him alone I see,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "All I need to cleanse and make me fully whole.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 40
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "In sorrow He's my comfort, in trouble He's my stay,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 46
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He tells me every care on Him to roll. Hallelujah !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 44
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He's the Lily of the Valley, the Bright and Morning Star,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 44
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He's the fairest of ten thousand to my soul.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "He all my griefs has taken, and all my sorrows borne;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 47
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "In temptation He's my strong and mighty tow'r;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 40
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I have all for Him forsaken, and all my idols torn",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 46
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "From my heart, and now He keeps me by His power.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 42
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Though all the world forsake me, and Satan tempt me sore,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 15
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 52
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Through Jesus I shall safely reach the goal. Hallelujah !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 50
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He's the Lily of the Valley, the Bright and Morning Star,"
    }, {
      "text" : "He's the fairest of ten thousand to my soul."
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "He'll never, never leave me, nor yet forsake me here,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 48
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "While I live by faith and do His blessed will;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "A wall of fire about me, I've nothing now to fear;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 45
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "With His manna He my hungry soul shall fill.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Then sweeping up to glory, we'll see His blessed face,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 49
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Where rivers of delight shall ever roll. Hallelujah !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 46
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He's the Lily of the Valley, the Bright and Morning Star,"
    }, {
      "text" : "He's the fairest of ten thousand to my soul."
    } ]
  } ]
}